Update on women's suffrage centennial events on Lebanon, Ohio television program

By Ohio Suffrage Centennial on February 26, 2020

On February 26, Katherine Durack returned to the Feelin’ Good program to update Shelly Abrams on all the events happening throughout Ohio and the United States for the 100th anniversary of women’s suffrage. Watch the interview on the Feelin’ Good website or YouTube and learn about all the great opportunities to celebrate women’s suffrage this year!

The Genius of Liberty podcast Katherine mentioned during this interview is available at SoundCloud. And here’s the Ohio Secretary of State’s Womens Suffrage Centennial intiative page!
